Study the past if you want to define the future.=C2=A0
Today, we are entering a new Techno-Economic Paradigm [ https://substack.co=
m/redirect/65e857cb-a917-422f-a28a-531cd126e085?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J=
5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ], like the one that Edison helped =
bring to life in the late 19th Century. General Electric was one of its big=
gest winners, because at a time when vertical integration was needed to fig=
