 compound.&#8221;&#160;</strong></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); fon=
t-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">That was certainly th=
e case for General Electric, whose market cap peaked near $500 billion in 2=
