=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); text-decoration: underline;">strategy</a><span>=
, part Techno-Economic Analysis.&#160;</span></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54,=
 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">On the s=
trategy side, there are questions to answer like: Why now? What is the bott=
leneck preventing incumbents from making their products better, faster, che=
