e: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><strong>Truly excellent fo=
unders are a compression algorithm.</strong><span>&#160;</span></p><p style=
=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0=
 20px 0;">If you judge that a founder is truly excellent &#8211; has the po=
tential to be an Edison, Rockefeller, Ford, Jobs, Huang, or Musk, which sou=
nds outlandish until you remember that theirs are the magnitude of company =
we&#8217;re after &#8211; that tells you almost everything else.&#160;</p><=
p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; marg=
in: 0 0 20px 0;">Most importantly, it will tell you whether they&#8217;re a=
ble to hire the team of people who are the best in the world at the particu=
lar thing they do that the company needs. Team is the only determinant of a=
bility to execute.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: =
16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><strong>You will not get cert=
ainty early in the life of a Vertical Integrator. You won&#8217;t get early=
 signs of product-market fit. You won&#8217;t get growth and retention curv=
es. You&#8217;ll just get a plan, one that probably sounds a little crazy, =
and some people. It&#8217;s up to you to decide whether to bet on their abi=
lity to execute.&#160;</strong></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font=
-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>Which raises the=
 obvious question: </span><strong>what makes a truly excellent founder?</st=
rong><span>&#160;</span></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: =
16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">There is no simple answer. Li=
ke porn, you know it when you see it.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 5=
5, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>Some=
times, all the things that make a founder great are present in one person, =
and sometimes, they&#8217;re present in a combination of co-founders. You c=
an read the great </span><a href=3D"https://substack.com/redirect/fddafe19-=
3dc5-4f5a-b813-334af11281dc?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXe=
pKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU" rel style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); text-decoration: =
underline;">Tablet profile on Palmer Luckey</a><span>, the Isaacson books o=
n </span><a href=3D"https://substack.com/redirect/6e743ecc-4025-4d82-8e9f-f=
5f594c06950?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkR=
NpU" rel style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); text-decoration: underline;">Elon=
 Musk</a><span> or </span><a href=3D"https://substack.com/redirect/14defd0f=
-35bb-49d9-8f8e-40db262ceb2c?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXX=
epKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU" rel style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); text-decoration:=
 underline;">Steve Jobs</a><span>, the recent Fortune article on </span><a =
href=3D"https://substack.com/redirect/69be4a8c-385d-48f5-a917-6049c333f2d6?=
j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU" rel sty=
le=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); text-decoration: underline;">Meter&#8217;s Va=
ranasi Brothers</a><span>, any of the profiles of the Collison Brothers, or=
 listen to the </span><a href=3D"https://substack.com/redirect/b897e1b8-639=
9-4d02-a818-beb7e84b1a17?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKb=
qOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU" rel style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); text-decoration: und=
erline;">Founders Podcast</a><span> episodes on history&#8217;s greatest fo=
unders and come away with different ideas of what a truly exceptional found=
er looks like.&#160;</span></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-siz=
e: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>As I was writing thi=
s, I came across this paragraph in </span><em>Empires of Light:</em></p><bl=
ockquote style=3D"border-left: 4px solid #0c2427; margin: 20px 0; padding: =
0;"><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px;=
 margin: 0 0 20px 0; margin-left: 20px;"><em>Unlike Edison, who launched hi=
s every new invention with maximum public ballyhoo, George Westinghouse int=
roduced his lighting revolution very quietly. No press account heralded the=
 tremendous breakthrough of AC, the bursting of the DC shackles. The AC rev=
olution began quietly and almost invisibly.</em><span>&#160;</span></p></bl=
ockquote><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: =
26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Two truly exceptional founders competing in the =
same industry at the same time in the same part of the world, and on the su=
rface, their approaches are diametrically opposed. There is no playbook or =
right answer. That&#8217;s the beauty.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, =
55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">That said=
, there are some things that seem to be present in most great founders:&#16=
0;</p><ul style=3D"margin-top: 0; padding: 0;"><li style=3D"margin: 8px 0 0=
 32px; mso-special-format: bullet;"><p style=3D"box-sizing: border-box; col=
or: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0; margin-=
bottom: 0; padding-left: 4px;">Ability to attract and pull the best out of =
world-class people.</p></li><li style=3D"margin: 8px 0 0 32px; mso-special-=
format: bullet;"><p style=3D"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(54, 55, 55)=
; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-=
left: 4px;">Deep curiosity and bottomlessly nuanced knowledge.&#160;</p></l=
i><li style=3D"margin: 8px 0 0 32px; mso-special-format: bullet;"><p style=
=3D"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-h=
eight: 26px; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-left: 4px;">Bias towards =
action and iteration.</p></li><li style=3D"margin: 8px 0 0 32px; mso-specia=
l-format: bullet;"><p style=3D"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(54, 55, 5=
5); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 0; paddin=
g-left: 4px;">Resilience and adaptability.&#160;</p></li><li style=3D"margi=
n: 8px 0 0 32px; mso-special-format: bullet;"><p style=3D"box-sizing: borde=
r-box; color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: =
0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-left: 4px;">Storytelling and fundraising.&#160=
;</p></li><li style=3D"margin: 8px 0 0 32px; mso-special-format: bullet;"><=
p style=3D"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px;=
 line-height: 26px; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-left: 4px;">Tirele=
ss work ethic and energy.</p></li><li style=3D"margin: 8px 0 0 32px; mso-sp=
ecial-format: bullet;"><p style=3D"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(54, 5=
5, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 0; pa=
dding-left: 4px;">Real commitment to a larger mission and desire to solve a=
 big puzzle.&#160;</p></li><li style=3D"margin: 8px 0 0 32px; mso-special-f=
ormat: bullet;"><p style=3D"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(54, 55, 55);=
 font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-l=
eft: 4px;">Ability to hold the whole system in their heads, from 30,000 fee=
t to one inch.&#160;</p></li></ul><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-=
size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>There&#8217;s som=
ething else about Vertical Integrator founders I&#8217;ve noticed that is c=
ounterintuitive: </span><strong>they often don&#8217;t come from within the=
 industry they&#8217;re trying to reshape.</strong><span>&#160;</span></p><=
p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; marg=
in: 0 0 20px 0;">Most haven&#8217;t studied one particular technology in sc=
hool that they&#8217;ll apply to the new problem. They&#8217;re definitely =
technical &#8211; at least one person on the founding team has to be able t=
o hold the whole system in their heads &#8211; but they&#8217;re more gener=
ally technical, in a &#8220;that guy can figure anything out&#8221; kind of=
 way.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-he=
ight: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">This actually makes a lot of sense. Vertic=
al Integrators need to figure out an entirely new way to do something that&=
#8217;s been done a certain way for years, and they need to do it with whic=
hever technologies and processes work best as part of the entire system. Be=
ing wedded, or even biased, to one way of doing things or one technology du=
lls the advantage of starting fresh.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55=
, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">There are e=
xceptions to everything I&#8217;ve just written, of course. There are commo=
n traits I&#8217;m missing, and the actual effect of the combination of tho=
se characteristics in a person is hard to describe.&#160;</p><p style=3D"co=
lor: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px =
0;"><span>If I had to sum it up, it&#8217;s something like: </span><strong>=
they make world-class people want to do their best work for them. </strong>=
<span>That&#8217;s a hard thing to capture in words or lists.&#160;</span><=
/p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; =
margin: 0 0 20px 0;">All of which is to say: underwriting Vertical Integrat=
ors is so difficult because to a large extent, it comes down to judging peo=
ple against the Herculean tasks they&#8217;ve set for themselves based on c=
lues but no certainties.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-=
size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">This is true to an exte=
nt for every startup investment. But the challenges are compounded with Ver=
tical Integrators for a few reasons:</p><ol style=3D"margin-top: 0; padding=
: 0;"><li style=3D"margin: 8px 0 0 32px;"><p style=3D"box-sizing: border-bo=
x; color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0; m=
argin-bottom: 0; padding-left: 4px;">These are harder, more complex compani=
es to build than typical startups.</p></li><li style=3D"margin: 8px 0 0 32p=
x;"><p style=3D"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: =
16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-left: 4px;">T=
he thing the founder is proposing has never been done.</p></li><li style=3D=
"margin: 8px 0 0 32px;"><p style=3D"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(54, =
55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 0; p=
adding-left: 4px;">They may require decades-long commitments to come to fru=
ition, with no easy outs along the way.&#160;</p></li><li style=3D"margin: =
8px 0 0 32px;"><p style=3D"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(54, 55, 55); =
font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-le=
ft: 4px;">They require more capital upfront to even have a shot, which mean=
s you need to decide before seeing how all of the pieces fit together in pr=
