ze: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">At some point, with enoug=
h proven, the valuation snaps violently into line with the size of the oppo=
rtunity. It flips from deeply improbable to somewhat probable, even obvious=
=2E SpaceX and Anduril have more demand=
 for their shares than they can meet,=20=
and enough capital to do what they need to do.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: =
rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">T=
he trick is figuring it out before it becomes obvious, when the capital is =
