gb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">We=
 will see cheap, abundant energy, cures for our most deadly diseases, super=
sonic flight, robots that do our chores, cars that drive us, homes people c=
an afford, adventures in space, and much more besides.&#160;</p><p style=3D=
"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20=
px 0;">But are these companies that create these miracles venture backable?=
 I think they&#8217;re among the only companies that are.&#160;</p><p style=
=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0=
 20px 0;">That may be a controversial thing to say, when new AI-powered Saa=
S companies are hitting $10s of millions of revenue in the first year while=
 Vertical Integrators take years and $10s of millions of dollars to get to =
first revenue, but it&#8217;s important to remember that it takes 7-10 year=
s, at a minimum, to get to IPO.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55)=
; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>One questi=
on you need to ask is: </span><strong>with everything changing as fast as i=
t is, do I see this company surviving and continuing to grow a decade from =
now?</strong><span>&#160;</span></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); fon=
t-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">That&#8217;s a hard q=
uestion to answer for companies that catch fire early and attract waves of =
competitors with the tools to build products in days that would have taken =
months.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-=
height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>Vertical Integrators are the oppos=
ite bet. They&#8217;re more uncertain and capital intensive early, but thos=
e things flip with time. As Ian Rountree wrote in </span><em><a href=3D"htt=
ps://substack.com/redirect/c9110324-f21a-41e2-acf5-c057c96deb32?j=3DeyJ1Ijo=
iOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU" rel style=3D"color=
: rgb(54, 55, 55); text-decoration: underline;">Full-Stack Deep Tech</a><sp=
an>.</span></em></p><blockquote style=3D"border-left: 4px solid #0c2427; ma=
rgin: 20px 0; padding: 0;"><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 1=
6px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0; margin-left: 20px;"><em><strong=
>Though full-stack startups may initially be more capital intensive we beli=
eve that they are ultimately more capital efficient</strong><span>.</span><=
/em></p></blockquote><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; l=
ine-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Once Vertical Integrators prove that=
 they can do what they say they&#8217;re going to do, they unlock access to=
 non-dilutive financing and practically bottomless markets with very little=
 competition. It may take 7-10 years to start generating meaningful revenue=
, but it&#8217;s much easier to imagine these companies being around in a c=
entury once they do.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size=
: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Their longevity means clear=
er paths to big outcomes, and the dependability to become platforms themsel=
ves.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-hei=
ght: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Just as Edison and Westinghouse laid the wi=
ring for a surge of businesses newly possible and improved by reliable elec=
tricity, the Vertical Integrators that bring this new Techno-Economic Parad=
igm into being will become a platform for entirely new businesses.&#160;</p=
><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; ma=
rgin: 0 0 20px 0;">This is already happening with SpaceX &#8211; a big part=
 of the &#8220;why now?&#8221; for every space startup &#8211; and it&#8217=
;s not hard to imagine that there will be thousands of businesses made poss=
ible by cheaper energy, faster construction, faster travel, longer, healthi=
er lives, better food, and automated manufacturing and labor, even if it&#8=
217;s hard to imagine exactly what those businesses will look like.&#160;</=
p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; m=
argin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>These businesses &#8211; the Vertical Integrators=
 and the new businesses they make possible &#8211; will benefit humanity as=
 much or more than the Industrial Revolution and the Second Industrial did.=
 With </span><a href=3D"https://substack.com/redirect/e90d8fa1-1b35-4c5c-9d=
fe-263766a630ad?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8=
ExkRNpU" rel style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); text-decoration: underline;">=
better tools</a><span>, and faster progress, we can solve ever-harder chall=
enges.&#160;</span></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px;=
 line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>But if history is a guide, <=
/span><strong>none will capture more value than the intrepid Vertical Integ=
rators that figure out how these new tools fit together and set the stage f=
or the half-century to come. </strong><span>&#160;</span></p><p style=3D"co=
lor: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px =
0;">That doesn&#8217;t mean it will be easy. In fact, it will be very, very=
 hard. There will be billion-dollar flameouts and promising technologies th=
at get punched in the mouth by manufacturing.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: r=
gb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Bu=
t some will make it through, and they will be very valuable, both financial=
ly and societally.&#160; Stay tuned for the Deep Dives to hear the stories =
of the ones to which I assign the highest probabilities in real-time.&#160;=
</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px;=
 margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Ultimately, the companies that bring these miracles i=
nto existence will be rightly rewarded for doing so, for they will have def=
ined and improved the future. It&#8217;s time to vertically integrate.&#160=
;</p><div style=3D"font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px;"><hr style=3D"backgr=
ound: #e6e6e6; border: none; height: 1px; margin: 32px 0; padding: 0;"></di=
